### TESTES DAS APIS DE FUTEBOL ###

### 1. Próximos jogos de um time específico
GET http://localhost:3000/api/fixtures/next?teamId=131&next=3
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Próximos jogos da liga (Série A)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/fixtures/league?leagueId=71&season=2025&next=10
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Classificação da Série A
GET http://localhost:3000/api/standings?leagueId=71&season=2025
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Buscar times por nome
GET http://localhost:3000/api/teams/search?name=Palmeiras&league=71
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Dados de um time específico
GET http://localhost:3000/api/teams/131
Content-Type: application/json

### 6. Mídia de um time (logo, escudo)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/media/team?name=Palmeiras
Content-Type: application/json

### 7. Endpoint combinado (dados completos do time)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/teams/combined?name=Palmeiras&next=2
Content-Type: application/json

### TESTES DE ERRO ###

### 8. Erro - teamId ausente
GET http://localhost:3000/api/fixtures/next
Content-Type: application/json

### 9. Erro - teamId inválido
GET http://localhost:3000/api/fixtures/next?teamId=abc
Content-Type: application/json

### 10. Erro - nome do time ausente
GET http://localhost:3000/api/media/team
Content-Type: application/json

